The USB ID in this entry is taken from the [http://www.iodata.jp/lib/product/w/4286.htm driver set] for the [[I-O_DATA_WN-AC867U|'''I-O DATA''' WN-AC867U]]. :<small>'''NEC AtermWL900U(PA-WL900U) Wireless Network Adapter'''</small> is the device description for the adapter.
This device is assumedly strictly distributed in the Japanese market.
